languages.text: "Сначала я убью тебя. Потом заберу твой трофей. А уж потом... Посмотрим, что я сделаю с твоим любимым Империумом".
"First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."
languages.original_text: "Сначала я убью тебя. Потом заберу твой трофей. А уж потом... Посмотрим, что я сделаю с твоим любимым Империумом".

traits.locale_text: "I will kill you first. Then, I will take your trophy for myself. And then... We will see what is going to happen to your lovely Imperium"

languages.text: « Je vais commencer par vous tuer, puis je m'emparerai de votre trophée. Ensuite.... nous verrons ce que je déciderai de faire de votre cher Imperium. »
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."

traits.locale_text: « Je vais commencer par vous tuer, puis je m'emparerai de votre trophée. Ensuite.... nous verrons ce qu'il adviendra de votre cher Imperium. »

languages.text: «Primero, te mataré. Después, me quedaré con tu trofeo. Y luego... veré qué hago con tu precioso Imperium».
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."

traits.locale_text: «Primero te mataré. Después, me quedaré con tu trofeo. Y luego... veremos qué le ocurre a tu querido Imperium».

languages.text: “我打算先杀了你，之后把你的战利品据为己有。到了那个时候……我可以好好想想，该打算如何处置你珍视的帝国。”
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."

traits.locale_text: “我打算先杀了你，之后把你的战利品据为己有。到了那个时候……我们可以看看，你珍视的帝国会面临怎样的下场。”

languages.text: "Zunächst einmal töte ich Euch. Dann nehme ich mir Eure Trophäe. Und dann ... sehen wir, was ich mit Eurem geliebten Imperium mache."
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."

traits.locale_text: "Vorher töte ich Euch. Dann nehme ich mir Eure Trophäe. Und dann ... Dann werden wir sehen, was mit Eurem geliebten Imperium geschieht."

languages.text: 「まず、お前を殺す。次に、お前の戦利品をもらい受ける。それから…お前の大切な帝国をどうするか、考えるとするか」
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."

traits.locale_text: 「まず、お前を殺す。次に、お前の戦利品をもらい受ける。それから…お前の大切な帝国をどうするか、考えるとするか」

languages.text: "Önce sizi öldüreceğim. Sonra ganimeti ele geçireceğim. Ardından... Değerli İmparatorluk'unuzla ne yapacağıma bakarım."
languages.original_text: "First, I will kill you. Then I will claim your trophy for myself. And then... we shall see what I will do to your precious Imperium."
